&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What is saas.group?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Think of us as the driving catalyst behind your favorite software success stories. saas.group, established in 2017, is on a mission to turbocharge promising B2B SaaS ventures, unlocking their full potential. As a Software-as-a-Service portfolio powerhouse, we specialize in acquiring small software treasures and polishing them into industry stars. With a dynamic, fully remote team of nearly 400 colleagues spanning 50+ countries we are truly global and we are rewriting the playbook on SaaS innovation and collaboration. We grow &lt;a href=&quot;https://saas.group/family/&quot;&gt;25 exciting brands&lt;/a&gt; under our umbrella. Feel free to explore our &lt;a href=&quot;https://saas.group/candidate-hub/&quot;&gt;Candidate&#39;s Hub&lt;/a&gt; to get an insider&#39;s view, dive into our culture, gain valuable insights into our teams and how we work.&lt;/p&gt;
