&lt;p&gt;You will take full ownership of how we grow MRR, build our brand presence, and take our product to our existing and new users.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity to step into a product with deep market credibility and 800,000+ users and have a real impact on its next growth chapter.&lt;/p&gt;
