&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generalist growth marketing background: you connect the dots across channels and data, find creative angles, and make things happen without waiting for perfect conditions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SEO expertise: deep enough to lead strategy for a product in the SEO tool space, navigate the market with authority, and credibly represent us to the SEO community and our users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI-native builder: you routinely use AI to work and to build — tools, automations, prototype

&lt;p&gt;This role is part of our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.infonline.de/&quot;&gt;INFOnline&lt;/a&gt; team, one of our exciting brands at saas.group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;INFOnline powers digital audience measurement for the German and Austrian media industry. Our systems process billions of events and deliver the trusted reach and engagement metrics used by publishers, advertisers, agencies, IVW and OEWA.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of saas.group, we have been modernizing our business-critical infrastructure and moving towards a fully cloud-native architecture on GCP. The major migration work is complete. Now we are looking for a strong technical owner to run, harden, scale and evolve the new platform.&lt;/p&gt;
