&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of core platform components from data ingress to reporting, supported by structured knowledge transfer where needed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish full internal ownership of the new cloud-native data platform&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve data quality controls, validation processes and operational safeguards&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a pragmatic post-migration roadmap focused on stability, scalability, data quality, cost efficiency and business continuity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strengthen monitoring, alerting, and observability for business-critical data workflows and IVW/OEWA delivery pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish engineering standards around documentation, code reviews, testing and AI-native development practices&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
